# Copy to `.cagevars` (gitignored, like `.env`). Non-secret, local
# `ctx-cage` sandbox-inclusion config ‚Äî distinct from `.env`, which is
# reserved for the summarizer's ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (ADR-013) and must
# never hold this kind of value or vice versa. Loaded automatically
# from the invocation CWD before every `ctx-cage`/`ctx-run` session; a
# value already set in the process environment always wins over this
# file.

# Colon-separated extra host directories to RO-bind into the cage and
# add to PATH (e.g. a tool installed outside /usr, /bin, or the Rust
# toolchain homes already bound automatically). Each entry must be a
# directory (not the binary itself) ‚Äî an entry that isn't a directory
# fails the run with an error rather than being silently dropped.
# CTX_CAGE_EXTRA_PATH=
